data.name: pictureBox1.ToolTip
data.value:
Story: You are a demon hunting Knight, on a new adventure that you were assigned while at the cavern. As you begin to head on your new adventure, a raven drops a letter by your feet, in it says that your beloved princess was captured by the Daedra King himself, you must journey across all 5 stages to rescue your distressed princess.
How to play: To fight you must use the left mouse click aimed at the monster. Once the monsters health reaches 0 the next stage opens. If the timer hits 0, the monster attacks you and you loose a life. You have 3 lives.
